comments: The patterns were inconsistent. "The" was used for both blue and grey, with it being random whether this was marked correct or not. The words were presented far too fast to take them in properly. No time was allowed to concentrate. The written words did not always match what was spoken. As a result of all these inconsistencies and the ridiculous speed of the presentation, no strategies were possible. I work as a translator out of seven languages, but I was unable to cope with this ridiculous study!
